Package: MetaPlasticScore
Title: Pipeline For Computing A "Plastic Degradation Potential Score And Plot"
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Gaetano", "Aufiero", , "gaetano.aufiero@unina.it", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: MetaPlasticScore is designed to estimate the potential for plastic degradation from metagenomic data. The package integrates enzyme annotation results from HMMER (hmmsearch) with taxon abundance profiles and metadata to compute a plastic score and plots.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
